{"tid":1213876,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"現時警察的基礎構成與當年六四的軍隊驚人地相似","createTime":"2019-06-13T03:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T08:29:33.000Z","uid":94441,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e34ab5689e2a7353fabe0e9f5db440ecd69169ca","tid":1213876,"uid":94441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:00:06.000Z","msg":"現時警察與當年六四執行屠殺命令的山西第27軍一樣，都係以（相對）低學歷人士為主。<br />\n<br />\n「按各部門聘請員佐職級人數資料統計，過去5個年度，警員一職吸納最多大學生，錄取的4,537名警員當中，有1,102人具備大學或以上學歷，佔整體獲聘警員約20%，包括去年度聘請250名大學生任職警員，較2012/13年度的197人增加近27%。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">換言之，2012-2017入職的警員約80%都只持專上/中學/毅進的學歷。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n「1989年6月5日，即軍隊鎮壓翌日，英國駐華大使唐納德發電報回倫敦，詳述一名中國國務院的成員提供的情報指，執行「暴行」（atrocities）的是來自<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">山西第27軍，當中60%是低學歷人士</span></span>。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsouce：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/123866/%E7%B4%80%E5%BE%8B%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E5%8F%96%E9%8C%84-%E5%93%A1%E4%BD%90%E7%B4%9A%E5%AD%B8%E6%AD%B7%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83-%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E8%99%95%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98-%E9%81%9455\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F123866%2F%25E7%25B4%2580%25E5%25BE%258B%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%258F%2596%25E9%258C%2584-%25E5%2593%25A1%25E4%25BD%2590%25E7%25B4%259A%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%25B8%2583-%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583%25E8%2599%2595%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25AF%2594%25E4%25BE%258B%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%2598-%25E9%2581%259455&d=OjLoGj31iMtRFsPqVtgEmurBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=e89ebf26\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/123866/%E7%B4%80%E5%BE%8B%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E5%8F%96%E9%8C%84-%E5%93%A1%E4%BD%90%E7%B4%9A%E5%AD%B8%E6%AD%B7%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83-%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%8